# Tip Calculator – Project Specification

## 1. Goal
Create a web-based tip calculator where users enter:
- Bill amount
- Tip percentage

The backend calculates and returns:
- Tip amount
- Total amount

## 2. Users
Public web app – no login.

## 3. Tech Stack
- Backend: Java + Spring Boot (REST API)
- Frontend: HTML/CSS + Vanilla JS (calls API)
- Hosting: Local or on Render

## 4. Features
- Input form
- Call backend `/calculate-tip`
- Show results dynamically